{"tid":1221561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急置頂）唔好中計，放風係等人唔參加616遊行，火力全開直至撤回","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:16:33.000Z","uid":142348,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1f8ece67f1213a6216250174eb52a4915fece3","tid":1221561,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"明大家思想皮勞 都想階段勝利下<br />\n大家想鬆可以去搵下唯唯位置<br />\n可以去反修訂大聯盟到鬆下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但必須大力攻入中產中層聲音<br />\n唔好俾政府發放嘅假消息影響<br />\n咩建制議員又放風又盛<br />\n<br />\n冇嘢係可信<br />\n係共產黨面前講信？？？<br />\n佢真係出嚟講話撤我就信<br />\n<br />\n唔要階段勝利 淨係要撤回<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d125a7b4eb45b5b3300e291bfaf67978510d9d4","tid":1221561,"uid":142348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"已經leng過嘢架啦雨傘 拖拖下就出事<br />\n咪俾佢陰到 ！"},{"pid":"6dcd68ee16e1b7ac64caaa13b45b83905289e3c1","tid":1221561,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"推吖屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a789317570da00e85f1d64c9c38e53494013c","tid":1221561,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dbd41